_header: Worldly aught is I-won with swink and sweating
_description: On the Vanity of Worldly possessions — three rhyming lines

CamEmm27.Transcription:
Worldlih eȝte is ywonne mid svynk and svetingeAnd hit is iloked
                    mid areȝe drediggeAnd furlete me hit schal mid soroȝe and
                    mornigge

James,  Montague Rhodes.
